, A., Woodward, S., Screening for resistance to Seiridium cardinale S. cupressi and S. unicorne isolates in glasshouse-grown seedlings of Cupressaceae (2001) Silvae Genetica, 50, pp. 258-264; Spanos, K.A., Pirrie, A., Woodward, S., Xenopoulos, S., responses in the bark of Cupressus sempervirens clones artificially inoculated with Seiridium cardinale under field conditions (1999) European Journal of Forest Pathology, 29, pp. 135-142; Suleman, P., Al-Musallam, A., Menezes, C.A., The effect of solute potential and water stress on black scorch caused by Chalara paradoxa and Chalara radicilora on date palms (2001) Plant Disease, 85, pp. 80-83; Tisserat, N.A., Nus, A., Barnes, L.W., A canker disease of the Cupressaceae in Kansas and Texas caused by Seiridium unicorne (1991) Plant Disease, 75, pp. 138-140; Tylianakis, J.M., Didham, R.K., Bascompte, J., Wardle, D.A., Global change and species interactions in terrestrial ecosystems (2008) Ecology Letters, 11, pp. 1351-1363; Vercesi, A., Tornaghi, R., Sant, S., Burruano, S., Faoro, F., A cytological and ultrastructural study on the maturation and germination of oospores of Plasmopora viticola from overwintering vine leaves (1999) Mycological Research, 103, pp. 193-202; Xenopoulos, S.G., Pathogenic variability of various isolates of Seiridium cardinale, S. cupressi and S. unicorne inoculated on selected Cupressus clones and seedlings (1991) European Journal of Forest Pathology, 21, pp. 129-135; Zocca, A., Zanini, C., Aimi, A., Frigimelica, G., La Porta, N., Battisti, A., Spread of plant pathogens and associated vectors at the northern range margin of cypress in Italy (2008) Acta Oecologica, 33, pp. 307-313","Turco, E.; Istituto per la Protezione delle Piante, Consiglio Nazionale delle ricerche (CNr), Via Madonna del Piano 10, 50019 Sesto Fiorentino (Firenze), Italy; email: e.turco@ipp.cnr.it",,,,,,,,00319465,,,,"English","Phytopathologia Mediterranea",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-79960095382
